{
  "stem": "6966.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you wake up in the night and you gotta do a pee-- in the corner of the barrack, you had a-- a kind of a barrel, or a container-- you sometimes stepped on a shoe and it was out of order.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if he came along while you were asleep or early morning before he woke you up, and he saw it, 24 men came out and they were beaten up.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we said to one another, boys, when you go out of the bed, put your shoes back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It'll save us being beaten up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then we slept under blankets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, I slept under a blanket.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I've never been under a blanket like that before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A lovely, thick, woolen blanket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And on there, I saw a piece of cloth sewn with a name of somebody in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I didn't know who or what it was-- of a man or a woman who had taken it along and he was no more.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But the blankets were given to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Later on, we get those thin blankets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But that I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I didn't realize what was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We'd get starved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We'd get very, very little food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember there were white enamel mugs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And in there was something white.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And you had to drink that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "During the day, you had four or five little potatoes in-- with peels, boiled in their peels.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That was your meal in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I remember that one day, we-- we only got about three potatoes, and we were grumbling.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the 50 men were stuck-- still together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one of them said, I noticed that's a barrack of the gypsies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You all keep a watch.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
